detailstable: Sony KDL-32W600D TV is made with narrow bezel to give the whole attention to the screen not the frame. It truly fits the home decoration, especially when you mount it on the wall.

This HD TV features X-Reality PRO which is the latest technology from Sony. It helps deliver pictures with refined details. Also, X-Reality Pro can enhance the low resolution content and upgrade it to a high immersive resolution.
Reach the maximum entertainment with this smart TV. You can check the web, watch videos on YouTube, watch online movies and more.
Share The Mobile Content On Sony TV
You will share the smartphone content on Sony TV through Screen Mirroring. You can share photos, videos and all your favorite memories.
